Name: Babysitter Simulator
About the game: But how much do you like children? Babysitter Simulator is a casual game which prepares you for mature life! Your mission seems simple at first sight, but it is not so. You should be the babysitter of 2 children, Emma and Liam. Together with them, you will learn to be a real babysitter, because you will must to learn them, wash, cook for them and many more. Game features : - A lot of babysitting activities like playing,washing,cooking,learning kids - 2 Kids that need attention - Parental sensations
